@dev Add 2 etec points on baby jubjub curve
x3 = (x1y2 + y1x2) * (z1z2 - dt1t2)
y3 = (y1y2 - ax1x2) * (z1z2 + dt1t2)
t3 = (y1y2 - ax1x2) * (x1y2 + y1x2)
z3 = (z1z2 - dt1t2) * (z1z2 + dt1t2)
